Name: Rise High
About the game: Rise High is an arcade action game in which you have to defend your workers from an alien invasion while they try to build skyscrapers! Collect power-ups and battle different kinds of aliens, rescue your workers from abductions and try to survive all 30 levels of old-school arcade action. Features single and two player coop mode - and as a fun little addtion a two player dogfight mode where you can try to shot you friend from the skies! 30 levels 3 difficulties Online leaderboards Bosses Infected buildings Controller and keyboard controls One and two player gameplay Achievements Steam trading cards
